  "texts": [
    "In accordance with design considerations, we allow users to choose unexplored tasks to be executed and delegate them to the agent.",
    "Additionally, users can remove pending tasks from the flow to reduce workload.",
    "A clear exploration structure may inspire user's ideas.Data table view: In addition to task visualization, we provide a data lens visualization in Data table view (Fig. 4D) to guide users in the large exploration space.",
    "When a task is being completed, the user can observe the exploration of the accumulated data usage frequency in table lens mode.",
    "The color of the table cell represents the relative frequency of each cell being explored."
  ],
